Exponential: Multiplicative

For \[y = \alpha e^{(\beta x + \epsilon)}\] with \(\epsilon \sim N(0,\sigma)\)

where

\[\begin{align*} xRange &= (0, 20)\\ N &= 20\\ \alpha & = \frac{1}{e^{\sigma^2/2}}\\ \end{align*}\]
